Description: UNIQUE -- No more than 1 enhancement of this type may be slotted by a character.  Gives the slotted power a chance to boost the user's damage slightly and reduces recharge time by {Boost.Attrib.Recharge.Scale}%.  This effect will trigger roughly 3 times per minute.  This enhancement can only be slotted by Dominators and may be slotted into most control powers.
DisplayName: Superior Attuned Superior Ascendency of the Dominator F
